/>\n唔太快決定<br />\n<br />\nBtw sony除左對焦快 仲有咩好處"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T16:27:05.000Z","msg":"一分錢一分貨<br />\n攝影界俾多$1000買個stabiliser都唔算多<br />\n電視台 blogger都係用sony唔係無原因<br />\nSony有咩好就上youtube自己睇啦<br />\n一大堆比較"},{"pid":"d0d8a933b1118bdb11f784b406dc0e83730fb905","tid":1990401,"uid":54066,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a53663dcdb2204776ba9510a6b7bea9fb04a0fc1","tid":1990401,"uid":53247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"12f9921cc0c4e079a5c5e36ebab61de7a653af08","tid":1990401,"uid":64571,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T15:56:51.000Z","msg":"唔好諗<br />\n直接買sony/nikon<br />\n利申10年olympus用家，已轉會"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T16:11:05.000Z","msg":"比多少少detail ok?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n身邊都有fd同我講唔好買olympus 但點解<br />\n近一個星期先開始睇下資料 唔太識<br />\n<br />\n我拍片為主  覺得防震效果唔錯先考慮"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T17:14:28.000Z","msg":"佢強既防震for 影相多，買個穩定器拍片會better<br />\n<br />\n拍片唔係唔得， 市場有更好選擇<br />\n就算m43 拍片都係panasonic 好過olympus<br />\n<br />\n如果真係拍片為主 sony aps 機加穩定器吧"},{"pid":"7530399d3adb03bfbe682bc269153da5838dae46","tid":1990401,"uid":208679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T17:33:25.000Z","msg":"Em10 m3開心使用中，呢個價位值得入，我自己個人覺得Olympus 色好靚,尤其om blue"},{"pid":"ea28c6ddd2cbeb2eabcfa7f1a5b233c791ddc573","tid":1990401,"uid":210506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T17:39:19.000Z","msg":"用m43拍片買gh5啦"},{"pid":"7b7fbad808cbe790a800afb97e8d2a0c410ae57d","tid":1990401,"uid":192736,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3ee04eeafc3fac5f05223b08456af1061a47af5e","tid":1990401,"uid":53247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T15:55:28.000Z","msg":"有冇用過olympus EM10 markiii 既巴打可以分享下<br />\n<br />\n打算主要拍片  續航幾耐  買水/行邊個比較好"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T17:59:00.000Z","msg":"用左好多年 o記 依家仲用緊<br />\nEm10 mk3<br />\n你預拍片 無headphone 返到去發現聲有事就麻煩<br />\n自己本身有用 em1 mk2 拍片 無大問題 因為防震夠勁<br />\n同好多時有落單腳架 <br />\n<br />\nO 記買行啦 因為水行價唔差太遠<br />\n<br />\nM43 黎講 p記拍片係勁 曾經有gh5 一段時間<br />\n但你又用唔用得晒d function 呢 如果你只係一般業餘玩下<br />\n<br />\n影相o記 無咩問題 因為我影人落燈<br />\n所以iso 都通常200 同studio 影好多時都唔追求淺景深<br />\n要淺景深 75mm f1.8 45mm f1.2 都夠<br />\n除非你真係要blur 到極致啦<br />\n<br />\n但講真 影相 邊有人張張都一味blur blur blur <br />\n<br />\nO記 防震勁 好多時 機(pen f) 加支15mm f1.7 都唔過700 g 輕便既快樂攝影"},{"pid":"f21c00368525db1a6370a7e399383a075dc33b73","tid":1990401,"uid":192736,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"12f9921cc0c4e079a5c5e36ebab61de7a653af08","tid":1990401,"uid":64571,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T15:56:51.000Z","msg":"唔好諗<br />\n直接買sony/nikon<br />\n利申10年olympus用家，已轉會"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T18:00:45.000Z","msg":"我都10 年用家 仲用得好開心<br />\n有咩問題 p記m43 好多業界人士都用 <br />\n証明m43 無問題"},{"pid":"99fb78624da81b238b4e8b54f716e97ebe1c71fe","tid":1990401,"uid":202340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T18:01:38.000Z","msg":"以前有部ep3 擺咗喺度好耐冇用過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n依家直接用手機"},{"pid":"7633b1a09033fe919e742ac248d01e2d6c80a45b","tid":1990401,"uid":256553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T00:52:40.000Z","msg":"拍片嚟講，em10 mk3呢個價位買g85可能好啲（而家呢個價真係無得輸）<br />\n基本上拍片要有嘅嘢佢都有<br />\n係對焦無pdaf嗰啲咁快"},{"pid":"6e7dc4101e52eb6f907f41491f5dcde688de3115","tid":1990401,"uid":53247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7633b1a09033fe919e742ac248d01e2d6c80a45b","tid":1990401,"uid":256553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T00:52:40.000Z","msg":"拍片嚟講，em10 mk3呢個價位買g85可能好啲（而家呢個價真係無得輸）<br />\n基本上拍片要有嘅嘢佢都有<br />\n係對焦無pdaf嗰啲咁快"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T01:27:12.000Z","msg":"研究下先 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好似幾正"},{"pid":"967415f1678a68cf4727f38bf3baea9de6d8c167","tid":1990401,"uid":267680,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T09:54:5