Z","msg":"有冇用過olympus EM10 markiii 既巴打可以分享下<br />\n<br />\n打算主要拍片  續航幾耐  買水/行邊個比較好"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T11:32:43.000Z","msg":"E-M10 III用家，如果主力拍片，真係間可以插外置咪的會好好多。同埋最好間些可以反mon出來的相機方便拍攝 ，MOONUTA@GMAIL.COM10III只能上下調整mon。"},{"pid":"1f76415110da10f09d5d72c98bf78a47bd3ef57e","tid":1990401,"uid":64571,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"f21c00368525db1a6370a7e399383a075dc33b73","tid":1990401,"uid":192736,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"12f9921cc0c4e079a5c5e36ebab61de7a653af08","tid":1990401,"uid":64571,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T15:56:51.000Z","msg":"唔好諗<br />\n直接買sony/nikon<br />\n利申10年olympus用家，已轉會"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T18:00:45.000Z","msg":"我都10 年用家 仲用得好開心<br />\n有咩問題 p記m43 好多業界人士都用 <br />\n証明m43 無問題"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T13:13:31.000Z","msg":"問題？無<br />\n正如我用iPhone咁一樣影得好開心<br />\n只係到你有部27吋 4k mon嘅時候<br />\n（事實係其實我一路都發現呢個問題，已經唔使什麼100%聞相）<br />\n睇相無論支鏡幾靚<br />\nm43條邊硬係唔實<br />\n我就知道呢個係物理限制，無得強求"},{"pid":"56549bf2f426dac078774eff735393b15d7e6e32","tid":1990401,"uid":53247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cec5446c389485d6a79c914b9496d3241d6262dc","tid":1990401,"uid":52459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3ee04eeafc3fac5f05223b08456af1061a47af5e","tid":1990401,"uid":53247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T15:55:28.000Z","msg":"有冇用過olympus EM10 markiii 既巴打可以分享下<br />\n<br />\n打算主要拍片  續航幾耐  買水/行邊個比較好"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T11:32:43.000Z","msg":"E-M10 III用家，如果主力拍片，真係間可以插外置咪的會好好多。同埋最好間些可以反mon出來的相機方便拍攝 ，MOONUTA@GMAIL.COM10III只能上下調整mon。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T13:26:55.000Z","msg":"有冇咩缺點你覺得係不能接受？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c165b71d6368426e4f7f8300466ec2b16cee4b3c","tid":1990401,"uid":186201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T13:29:37.000Z","msg":"O記拍片<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"